{"tid":1804241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［誠實豆沙包］嶺大研究：港人每年平均5.1日為非生病缺勤","createTime":"2019-12-31T00:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T04:44:09.000Z","uid":389,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e15f857d69c066e4a7049232f7c82dc2312a258a","tid":1804241,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T00:33:05.000Z","msg":"究竟點會話自己詐病呢？<br />\n<br />\n嶺南大學研究發現，本港僱員每年平均缺勤8.3日，其中因病請假佔3.2日，其餘5.1日為非生病缺勤。如按5.1日非生病缺勤來計算，即本港僱員平均每2至3個月，便有1天詐病請假或曠工。若以行業計，地產界平均缺勤率最高，每月非生病缺勤逾4日。<br />\n研究又表示，僱員工作壓力問題普遍，對社會及經濟帶來負面影響，每年總經濟損失達53至149億元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%B6%BA%E5%A4%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%875-1%E6%97%A5%E7%82%BA%E9%9D%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%97%85%E7%BC%BA%E5%8B%A4-201883\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25B6%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%25875-1%25E6%2597%25A5%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2597%2585%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E5%258B%25A4-201883&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=0db9476b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%B6%BA%E5%A4%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%9A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E6%AF%8F%E5%B9%B4%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%875-1%E6%97%A5%E7%82%BA%E9%9D%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%97%85%E7%BC%BA%E5%8B%A4-201883</a>"},{"pid":"41f4a1a56eab1d7720b73d9bb33a8468bd9fc1e1","tid":1804241,"uid":260296,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"香港人：請假 = 罷工"},{"pid":"47aab233861fd660f68f0ce6de5250f74f6c67fb","tid":1804241,"uid":165871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T00:36:17.000Z","msg":"病假當大假用是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1746a7c0cbd99908737d6a6fcfce31b39